metadata.name: endings and beginnings
metadata.description:
the end of an old era, and the beginning of a new one. when I first created this photo, it was during one of the wildest moments of growth I've ever had in my career, and as I mint this now I sit in a new moment of transition - moving onto a period of time where I can use these new lessons that have came, but returning to old priorities and values that I'm finding valuable once again. feeling inspired by art and music again, feeling hopeful for the future, but from a new perspective - and with new knowledge in mind.

to growth and a bright new future

- wgm v
